“General Manager” means the General Manager appointed under 
subsection 14(1) and includes a Deputy General Manager directed to 
perform the duties of the General Manager under subsection 14(7);

“Kawasan Lembaga Kemajuan Wilayah Pulau Pinang” means the 
area or areas  determined by the Minister in  accordance with  section 
10 to be the Kawasan Lembaga Kemajuan Wilayah Pulau Pinang;

